      skos:note "Quantification is staged honestly: one metric per engagement, instrumented in the calibration readouts; friendlies produce the first real numbers; engagement one's number is engagement two's pitch." ;
      narr:theme "Quantification is staged honestly — one metric per engagement; friendlies produce the first real numbers; engagement one's number is engagement two's pitch" .

